descriptionHtml: My Pub Crawl gives you access to all the information you require on every pub and bar in Liverpool. It comes with a brilliant interactive map for every pub crawl, plus get amazing offers and discounts at selected pubs and bars in Liverpool. Simply search by location or category and allow the app to be your guide.

creator: My Pub Crawl
descriptionHtml:
We are here to guide you around all the cities in the UK, for the best pub experience. We break each city down into multiple districts and each of them features an interactive map to help guide you around the area. There is also a category option with interactive maps and allows you to select a type of venue, such as Real Ale, Cocktail Bars, Bottomless Bruch, Live Music, Dog Friendly and many more!

This FREE app is the ultimate going out companion and acts as your own personal tour guide. Plus, as an added bonus, many of the venues offer between a 10-20% discount if you show the app at the bar! Whatever you like to do, our app will help you have the best day or night out possible.
title: My Pub Guide
